headline: Intuit Announces Annual Stockholder Meeting
summary: MOUNTAIN VIEW, Calif., January 15, 2026--Intuit Inc. (Nasdaq: INTU), the global financial technology platform that makes Intuit TurboTax, Credit Karma, QuickBooks, and Mailchimp, will hold its annual stockholder meeting virtually on Thursday, January 22 at 8:00 AM Pacific time.
